  <brief_title>Lactoserum (Dermacyd Femina速) and Prevention of Recurrence of Bacterial Vaginosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Local, National (Brazil), Multicentric, Open, Non-Controlled, Phase IV, Study of Lactoserum (Dermacyd Femina速), in Women at Reproductive Age, to Prevent Recurrence of Bacterial Vaginosis, During Three Months, After Standard Treatment With Metronidazole.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
