  <source>Sanofi</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to demonstrate if the use of Dermacyd can avoid the recurrence
      of bacterial vaginosis after three months of the standard treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
